This repository packages and distributes a developer container around the
official Qwen Code project.

Upstream project:
  https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code

This repository follows the upstream Qwen Code project for CLI behavior,
interaction model, and protocol compatibility. The work here focuses on:

- containerization
- deployment packaging
- field delivery documentation
- OpenAI-compatible runtime configuration

Acknowledgment:
Qwen Code is the upstream open-source terminal agent maintained by QwenLM.
This repository is not a replacement for the upstream project. It is a
delivery-oriented container wrapper intended to simplify deployment and
internal usage while preserving upstream usage semantics as much as possible.
